title.rendered: The Simpsons: Welcome to the Club

content.rendered:
It’s Disney+ day and Lisa Simpson is determined to turn into a princess. But some conniving Disney villains convince him that being bad is more fun.

Directed By David Silverman

Written By J. Stewart Burns. Joel H. Cohen. Al Jean

Stars: Nancy Cartwright. Yeardley Smith. Chris Edgerly
